body_html:
@martinwicke it looks good now, the only failure is //tensorflow/compiler/xla/tests:exhaustive_f32_elementwise_op_test_cpu which has been failing for a few weeks so is unrelated. :)

Also I've included this patchset (+protobuf unbundling which isnt part of this PR) in the Gentoo package for tensorflow-1.11.0_rc{0,1,2} and its working well so far.
